---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
    keywords="privacy policy, data protection, user rights, cookies, information security"
    title="Privacy Policy - CodeBrand Solutions"
    description="Privacy policy of CodeBrand Solutions. Information about the collection, use, and protection of personal data on our website and services. User rights and contact details."
>
    <section class="py-20 flex flex-col gap-20">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-cyan-900 text-center">
            Privacy Policy
        </h2>

        <div class="w-3/4 mx-auto text-lg text-gray-700 space-y-10">
            <p>
                At <strong>CodeBrand Solutions</strong>, we are committed to
                protecting the privacy and security of our website visitors and
                clients. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use,
                share, and protect personal information through the website <a
                    href="https://solutions.codebrand.es"
                    class="text-blue-600 underline">solutions.codebrand.es</a
                >.
            </p>

            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-cyan-800">
                1. Information We Collect
            </h3>
            <p>
                <strong>1.1 Information Provided by the User:</strong> When interacting
                with us or using our services, you may provide us with information
                such as:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
                <li>Full name</li>
                <li>Email address and phone number</li>
                <li>Company name, job title, and industry</li>
                <li>
                    Preferences, comments, or requests related to our services
                </li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                <strong>1.2 Information Collected Automatically:</strong> When browsing
                our website, we collect information through cookies and similar technologies,
                such as:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
                <li>IP address</li>
                <li>Browser and device information</li>
                <li>Pages visited and browsing time</li>
                <li>Approximate geographic location</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-cyan-800">
                2. Use of Information
            </h3>
            <p>We use the collected information for the following purposes:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
                <li>To provide, operate, and improve our digital services</li>
                <li>To personalize your experience on the site</li>
                <li>
                    To communicate with you about updates, news, and promotions
                </li>
                <li>To comply with legal obligations and resolve disputes</li>
                <li>
                    To conduct market analysis and continuously improve our
                    offerings
                </li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-cyan-800">
                3. Legal Basis for Processing
            </h3>
            <p>
                We process your personal data based on various legal grounds,
                depending on our relationship with you:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
                <li>
                    <strong>Consent:</strong> For cookies and direct marketing communications
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Contract performance:</strong> To provide requested services
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Legitimate interests:</strong> To improve our services
                    and communications
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Legal obligations:</strong> To comply with applicable
                    regulations
                </li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-cyan-800">
                4. International Transfers
            </h3>
            <p>
                In some cases, your data may be transferred and processed
                outside your jurisdiction. We ensure that such transfers are
                made with appropriate safeguards and in compliance with data
                protection laws.
            </p>

            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-cyan-800">5. User Rights</h3>
            <p>As the data subject, you have the following rights:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
                <li>Access your personal data</li>
                <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
                <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
                <li>Restrict or object to data processing</li>
                <li>Request data portability to another provider</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-cyan-800">
                6. Information Security
            </h3>
            <p>
                We implement technical and organizational measures to protect
                your personal data against unauthorized access, accidental loss,
                or destruction. This includes encryption, firewalls, and
                restricted access protocols.
            </p>

            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-cyan-800">
                7. Cookies and Tracking Technologies
            </h3>
            <p>
                We use cookies to analyze site usage, improve user experience,
                and offer personalized content. You can learn more and manage
                your preferences in our Cookie Policy.
            </p>

            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-cyan-800">
                8. Changes to This Policy
            </h3>
            <p>
                We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy at any time.
                Changes will be published on this page, and if they are
                significant, we will notify you prominently.
            </p>

            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-cyan-800">9. Contact</h3>
            <p>
                If you have any questions about this policy or wish to exercise
                your rights regarding your personal data, you can contact us at:
            </p>
            <p>
                <strong>CodeBrand Solutions</strong><br />Email:
                info@codebrand.es<br />Website: <a
                    href="https://solutions.codebrand.es"
                    class="text-blue-600 underline"
                    >https://solutions.codebrand.es</a
                >
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
